Welcome to Space Orb! We're glad you decided to download and use our app. In this document, you will find the information you need to start using the app and troubleshoot any issues you may encounter.

Getting Started:

Download the app from the App Store or Google Play Store.

Once the app is installed, open it and tap to begin!

Upon first playthrough, a brief tutorial will be shown

Troubleshooting:

If you're experiencing issues with the app crashing or freezing, try closing the app and reopening it. If the problem persists, try restarting your device.

If you're still experiencing issues and can't find a solution, please contact us via email at dohboygames@gmail.com.

We hope you enjoy using our app and we appreciate your support.
